{"id": "ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 93, "displayName": {"text": "Sushi Kyo", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOc2JXdEplV2t6TUY5V1lWaFBNM1l5Y0VkcldVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Super fresh and amazing quality sushi and more!  The menu is huge with assorted sushi, chirashi bowls, bento boxes, hand rolls, baked rolls, several inari choices, large boats filled with sushi for large groups, and non seafood items as well! The okonomiyaki tasted just like the ones in Osaka.  Staff are super nice and attentive.  They also provide complementary corn soup which was like eating a dissolves corn puff in the best way possible.  Everything was truly delicious and cannot wait to try more menu items.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super fresh and amazing quality sushi and more!  The menu is huge with assorted sushi, chirashi bowls, bento boxes, hand rolls, baked rolls, several inari choices, large boats filled with sushi for large groups, and non seafood items as well! The okonomiyaki tasted just like the ones in Osaka.  Staff are super nice and attentive.  They also provide complementary corn soup which was like eating a dissolves corn puff in the best way possible.  Everything was truly delicious and cannot wait to try more menu items.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amanda Potchanatayparuk", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102629987364925365749/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjqDbKM0QcGIWR_oCvu_KKVxtnqVVS_AVFH1chLldi-EEH4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T05:55:17.048851210Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOc2JXdEplV2t6TUY5V1lWaFBNM1l5Y0VkcldVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOc2JXdEplV2t6TUY5V1lWaFBNM1l5Y0VkcldVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d9c1397ecc11:0xe7ee3b7e7617cc80"}, {"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vd1NFRldjMEZtV1doYWREVkROVlJOT1hKalIzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "If you're looking for a Japanese restaurant that has amazing service, huge portions, and decent pricing for high quality food, this place is it. There are so many options on the menu, from sushi sets to bento combos, to making your own roll combos and assortments of rolls and sushi. Everything looked good! We got a lunch bento, a katsudon, spicy seafood ramen, tempura udon, okonomiyaki, salmon inari, and furikake fries. The fish was so fresh in the inari. The lunch bento was huge and the salad was a great complement to the fish and fried foods. The staff was super attentive and kept refilling our waters and teas. We got a corn soup as part of lunch as well. Only letdown was the okonomiyaki, which was a little mushy and could have been fried a little longer on both sides. But other than that, an excellent meal.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you're looking for a Japanese restaurant that has amazing service, huge portions, and decent pricing for high quality food, this place is it. There are so many options on the menu, from sushi sets to bento combos, to making your own roll combos and assortments of rolls and sushi. Everything looked good! We got a lunch bento, a katsudon, spicy seafood ramen, tempura udon, okonomiyaki, salmon inari, and furikake fries. The fish was so fresh in the inari. The lunch bento was huge and the salad was a great complement to the fish and fried foods. The staff was super attentive and kept refilling our waters and teas. We got a corn soup as part of lunch as well. Only letdown was the okonomiyaki, which was a little mushy and could have been fried a little longer on both sides. But other than that, an excellent meal.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amy Y", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106296843800541593082/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCHz6QMVZkDrDJw6k_zpjXMdiw-4Ctlo-DncbK-WSJ0NNcBlnW=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T03:54:32.638832976Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vd1NFRldjMEZtV1doYWREVkROVlJOT1hKalIzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21vd1NFRldjMEZtV1doYWREVkROVlJOT1hKalIzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d9c1397ecc11:0xe7ee3b7e7617cc80"}, {"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOeE5HTkliRzR6ZUMxMWRFSmlRelJTV1RGTlNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Sushi Kyo absolutely delivered this is one of those spots where you can tell they actually care about the food, not just the presentation (and the presentation is 🔥 too).\n\nEvery roll we ordered was fresh, balanced, and packed with flavor. The fish quality stood out immediately clean, buttery cuts with zero fishiness. The specialty rolls were next level… rich, slightly indulgent, but still super well executed. Nothing felt sloppy or overdone.\n\nThe yellowtail with jalapeño? 🔥 Perfect bite bright, clean, with just the right kick.\nAnd that hot dish with the egg on top (okonomiyaki-style)? Insane. Savory, comforting, and easily one of those dishes you think about after you leave.\n\nService was smooth, vibe was chill, and everything came out at a great pace. It’s the kind of place that works whether you’re doing a casual dinner or bringing people you want to impress.\n\nBottom line:\nIf you’re in Monrovia and want legit sushi that actually hits, Sushi Kyo is 100% worth it. I’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Sushi Kyo absolutely delivered this is one of those spots where you can tell they actually care about the food, not just the presentation (and the presentation is 🔥 too).\n\nEvery roll we ordered was fresh, balanced, and packed with flavor. The fish quality stood out immediately clean, buttery cuts with zero fishiness. The specialty rolls were next level… rich, slightly indulgent, but still super well executed. Nothing felt sloppy or overdone.\n\nThe yellowtail with jalapeño? 🔥 Perfect bite bright, clean, with just the right kick.\nAnd that hot dish with the egg on top (okonomiyaki-style)? Insane. Savory, comforting, and easily one of those dishes you think about after you leave.\n\nService was smooth, vibe was chill, and everything came out at a great pace. It’s the kind of place that works whether you’re doing a casual dinner or bringing people you want to impress.\n\nBottom line:\nIf you’re in Monrovia and want legit sushi that actually hits, Sushi Kyo is 100% worth it. I’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Now.Loading.Carlos", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101672671238479315219/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkFSHb9toVc_0vQ3Ajuk65ItkxBQwAIZEEIfJVjKaCwXEz92w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-28T03:43:18.912635572Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOeE5HTkliRzR6ZUMxMWRFSmlRelJTV1RGTlNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOeE5HTkliRzR6ZUMxMWRFSmlRelJTV1RGTlNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d9c1397ecc11:0xe7ee3b7e7617cc80"}, {"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM2JrY3pUMGswV2kxNFprMXNRVWxyT1hCRWVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here after work for lunch. It wasn't busy so I was seated quickly and my order taken. I ordered 2 spicy tuna rolls and 2 seared lime pepper salmon rolls. The taste of these rolls was amazing and the spice was perfect on them. I will definitely come back here again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here after work for lunch. It wasn't busy so I was seated quickly and my order taken. I ordered 2 spicy tuna rolls and 2 seared lime pepper salmon rolls. The taste of these rolls was amazing and the spice was perfect on them. I will definitely come back here again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Juana Martinez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116200156518800023850/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpguFNsoBizfMSvXMCC1iKQh8lqJMRGvCMouHO8UwpQUF54-KIEQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T21:47:18.726706598Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM2JrY3pUMGswV2kxNFprMXNRVWxyT1hCRWVrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkM2JrY3pUMGswV2kxNFprMXNRVWxyT1hCRWVrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d9c1397ecc11:0xe7ee3b7e7617cc80"}, {"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GVFdrZENTVlkzUVRkVVZHcDRORVZ6Wm5CRFZtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My new favorite sushi restaurant in Monrovia! It has dethroned Mikomi and Nakata for me.\n\nI ordered the main kyo box some rolls and Ala carte items.\n\nEverything tasted great and fresh. I think they have some operational kinks they need to work out. For example giving me the wrong receipt and order\n\nBut I love that they fix mistakes quickly\n\nI will be coming back again soon", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My new favorite sushi restaurant in Monrovia! It has dethroned Mikomi and Nakata for me.\n\nI ordered the main kyo box some rolls and Ala carte items.\n\nEverything tasted great and fresh. I think they have some operational kinks they need to work out. For example giving me the wrong receipt and order\n\nBut I love that they fix mistakes quickly\n\nI will be coming back again soon", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jessica Ju", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113892190063061696274/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInx83mEbFYMFR-duY_1w9tkUfEzgwL9wtQqL_TFd4GstxSgw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-16T19:49:30.101795887Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GVFdrZENTVlkzUVRkVVZHcDRORVZ6Wm5CRFZtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GVFdrZENTVlkzUVRkVVZHcDRORVZ6Wm5CRFZtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2d9c1397ecc11:0xe7ee3b7e7617cc80"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJEcx-OcHZwoARgMwXdn477uc/photos/AWCwydjejhOd3ntCZ90J7Yb_fUNP74wV3rAD8N_GOyN0eJG2tY2BHJWqYDOqEW8TQLfcYZQ8PjZPTJviNf_QAlk6TN2mFaowAxUjOUvOIpCSp9DAdYJ5m4WeyMfzOCNnh39B21xPjUixguFv5q0gIV-GW-g_WYD3YAwoLqI1Hp3R1xrwsf4nM_WZUUntj6L0OqCUOZG93EB5B7RzHYuXcMa0mUE1MBx_w_5oQ42jPMnAj_xKCFbUVZ217KzwnDiUKwRSc4VUOUkfTHMmmQI_ltsyHfTLy5tJ-NYpZ_KURmIVfXzQM_NhrzkKdOTFkyYWWAEvITuQHXZt4ijebPZVrkQQAYdKyR77uy5jfLUX1mjiaTaOKOiquc_mbGosiiKPyHyHjiQCDFg5QhA-k3m56fNKbhsXCXS-iuPGsFiVuWiNw9n7AK9gv5HdcFyjRZjy9wNa", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3599, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Sushi Kyo", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106228053998865833769", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMM9tATfqn4FhS_TQfXW48OHfHJ5SS9aky1I7fFrSBvkiGOAOA=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhA8wDbBXSGJX7lKteE30-EO&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhA8wDbBXSGJX7lKteE30-EO